   "source": [
    "from decimal import Decimal, getcontext\n",
    "\n",
    "getcontext().prec = 50  # Set \n",
    "def solve_quadratic (a,b,c):\n",
    "    a, b, c = Decimal(a), Decimal(b), Decimal(c)\n",
    "    d = (b**2) - (4*a*c)\n",
    "    sol1 = float((-b-np.sqrt(d))/(2*a))\n",
    "    sol2 = float((-b+np.sqrt(d))/(2*a))\n",
    "    return [sol1,sol2]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 72,
   "id": "b3ba2dbc",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def find_x_where_f_equals_g(a1, b1, c1, a2, b2, c2):\n",
    "    \n",
    "    \n",
    "    return solve_quadratic(a1-a2,b1-b2,c1-c2)"
   ]
  },
